Thank you for providing the details. Our team will review your business verification request and get back to you shortly. If there's anything else you need, feel free to ask!

For business verification issues, please ensure that you have provided all the necessary details in your email to adsupport@newsbreak.com. This includes your company's full address, legal entity name, EHID or DUNS number, primary contact person's name, and phone number. Once our team receives this information, they will conduct a thorough review and update you on your account status. If you have any other questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask!

I understand that you've already sent an email regarding the business verification issue. It can sometimes take a few days for our team to review and respond. If you don't hear back soon, please let me know, and I'll do my best to assist you further.
